<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations> <http://schema.org/name> "Organisations" .
_:Nc66328e40c1045acb9aa88cfa61dc55a <http://schema.org/articleBody> "<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>This publication scheme specifies the categories of information that the department and its agencies regularly publish and explains how to get that information. </p>\n\n<p>You can find specific documents for this department using the <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/search/transparency-and-freedom-of-information-releases?content_store_document_type=transparency&amp;keywords=&amp;organisations%5B%5D=office-of-manpower-economics\">publication search</a>. </p>\n\n<p>If the information you want is not routinely published, you can <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/make-a-freedom-of-information-request\">make a request for it</a>. You can also search through <a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/search/transparency-and-freedom-of-information-releases?content_store_document_type=foi_release&amp;keywords=&amp;world_locations%5B%5D=office-of-manpower-economics\">previous responses to freedom of information requests</a>.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"who-we-are-and-what-we-do\">Who we are and what we do </h2>\n\n<p>The information published within this category covers our organisational details, structures, locations and contacts. This includes: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies/about\">our roles and responsibilities</a> </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/office-for-the-pay-review-bodies#org-contacts\">our location and contact details</a> </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-we-spend-and-how-we-spend-it\">What we spend and how we spend it </h2>\n\n<p>In this category, we regularly publish financial information about projected and actual income, expenditure, procurement, contracts and financial audits. This includes: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/pay-review-body-members-fees-and-expenses\">fees and expenses paid to review body members</a></p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>Non-manual pay awards survey: available upon request </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"what-our-priorities-are-and-how-we-are-doing\">What our priorities are and how we are doing </h2>\n\n<p>This category covers our strategies and plans, performance indicators, audits, inspections and reviews, including: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/ome-stewardship-reports\">our annual stewardship reports</a> </p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>cross-cutting consultants’ reports: these will be published in full except where an exemption applies </p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"our-policies-and-procedures\">Our policies and procedures </h2>\n\n<p>This category covers our protocols, policies and procedures for delivering services and responsibilities, including: </p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Model framework agreement: available upon request</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"the-services-we-offer\">The services we offer</h2>\n\n<p>Requests for information must be made in writing by post or email, and sent to:</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact contact\" id=\"contact_6288\">\n    <p class=\"govuk-body\">General enquiries</p>\n\n    <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n      First floor, Caxton House, 6-12 Tothill Street<br>London<br>SW1H 9NA\n    </p>\n\n    <div>\n        <p class=\"govuk-body govuk-!-margin-bottom-4\">\n          Email <a class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"mailto:OPRB.enquiries@businessandtrade.gov.uk%20\">OPRB.enquiries@businessandtrade.gov.uk </a>\n        </p>\n\n\n    </div>\n\n\n</div>\n\n<h2 id=\"charges\">Charges</h2>\n\n<p>There will not be any charge for information requested and supplied from the publication scheme.</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"types-of-information-we-wont-publish\">Types of information we won’t publish</h2>\n\n<p>We generally won’t publish information that is:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <p>protected from disclosure</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>in draft form</p>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <p>no longer readily available</p>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n</div>" .
